author: @Damonistique
text:
This is such a creative way to introduce the album! Especially with the amazing instrumentals playing in the background.
Very... Jaehyun way to do it. I feel like he's a person who values sensory experience and tries to enjoy each moment to the fullest, so ASMR suite him, enriching the album experience.
I was stunned when he told about the details in Smoke and the vibe of watching through the rear window. It's a perfect way to describe it, a maze of mirrors in seemingly ordinary setting.
Also, there is something in a way he crushes rose petals for the desperate Roses...
Damn, I love him and his mind, the map of his soul. Thank you for sharing it with us.

text:
Why was I gagged by him simply lighting that match??? LOLOLOL. My mans is HAWTTTTT GOTDAMNNN. But uhhh... this man is def not afraid to catch that mic on fire. LOL. Rich man said don't worry, I'll cover it if I burn it. He kept getting so close lolololol. In all seriousness, Jaehyun's album is a straight banger. Listening to it honestly feels like a warm hug or that warm feeling on a cold winter day and we're cozied up on the couch with a blanket around us, all toasty and lost in thoughts or enjoying people watching. You can feel the genuineness in the lyrics and it's complimented so well with his voice which conveys such pure emotion. I just appreciate this album a lot and I'm thankful for the hard work everyone put in it. Because of you all, us fans get to enjoy perfection and have good memories. <3 Love you! Fighting!
